You can style your text quickly by using context menu. Some step follow now;
1. Type any text and long press then open menu.
2. Tap dot menu and select Style text option.
3. Choose any text style from the dialog.
Floating Bubble Style text feature to apply text style any app. Working process:
1. Turn on bubble by drawing over other apps
2. Tap floating bubble icon and apply any text style from the dialog
Style text is Text Converter tool thats help to convert simple text to fancy stylish text and you can share it. Stylish Nickname generator you can generate unique nickname use in game.
